It’s Thursday lunchtime, and what better time to tackle our new weekly quiz? It is made up of 15 teasing questions on general knowledge and topical news trivia. It is just for fun and there are no prizes, but do let us know how you get on in the comments below. The weekly Guardian quiz, No 1 If you think there has been an egregious error in one of the questions or answers, please feel free to email martin.belam@theguardian.com, but remember, the quizmaster’s word is always final.